                            19. 1.unsur intrinsik cerpen2.unsur ekstrinsik cerpen​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>-unsur</strong><strong> </strong><strong>intrinsik</strong><strong> </strong><strong>cerpen</strong></p><p>1.<strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>T</strong><strong>ema</strong></p><p>2. <strong>T</strong><strong>okoh</strong><strong>:</strong>protagonis,antagonis,tritagonis</p><p>    <strong>P</strong><strong>enokohan</strong><strong>:</strong>analitik,dramatik</p><p>3. <strong>Alur</strong><strong>:</strong>maju,mundur,campuran</p><p>4. <strong>Latar</strong><strong>:</strong>waktu,tempat,sosial,suasana</p><p>5. <strong>Sudut</strong><strong> </strong><strong>pandang</strong><strong>:</strong>orang |,||,|||</p><p>6.<strong> </strong><strong>Gaya</strong><strong> </strong><strong>bahasa</strong></p><p>7.  <strong>Amanat</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p>Semoga membantu:^</p><br />
